sequenceDiagram
  participant U as Atlas User
  participant API as Onyx API
  participant AUTH as Auth/Permissions
  participant RET as Retrieval Path
  participant TOOL as Tool/MCP Path
  participant OBS as Logging/Tracing

  U->>API: Submit prompt
  API->>AUTH: Resolve user + permissions
  AUTH-->>API: Allow or Deny
  alt Deny
    API-->>U: Fail-closed denial
    API->>OBS: Emit deny event (Partially Confirmed)
  else Allow
    API->>RET: Build query + apply ACL filter
    RET-->>API: Return candidate context
    API->>TOOL: Optional tool/MCP invocation
    TOOL-->>API: Tool result (Needs Verification)
    API-->>U: Final grounded response
    API->>OBS: Emit logs/trace/metrics
  end

  Note over RET: Unknown: complete ACL consistency across modalities
  Note over OBS: Unknown: policy decision log completeness in runtime
